            the San Francisco Bay. Our Services include:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Information about our conservation programs and initiatives</li>
            <li>Volunteer registration and coordination</li>
            <li>Donation processing through secure payment platforms</li>
            <li>Educational resources and content</li>
            <li>Newsletter subscriptions</li>
            <li>Contact forms for inquiries</li>
          </ul>
        </LegalSection>

