            All donations are final and non-refundable except in cases of processing errors. Bay
            Tides is a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization, and donations may be
            tax-deductible to the extent permitted by law. We will provide donation receipts for tax
            purposes automatically via email.
          </p>
        </LegalSection>

